        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Certificate issued by the faculty and president, James Madison, of the College of
                William and Mary and signed by James Monroe, Governor of Virginia. Richard Clements is
                appointed surveyor for Southampton County, Va. He is instructed to return one-sixth
                of all fees collected to the College faculty. Faculty members include Robert
                Andrews, John Bracken, and James Henderson. Printed form with manuscript insertions.
            </p>
        </scopecontent>
